From: Marcos <marcosbrendonaz@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 27 Mar 2026 02:49:59 -0300
Subject: [PATCH 14/15] feat: expand __chameleon API with full bot automation
 toolkit

14 functions available in isolated worlds:

Actions:
- click(el) - trusted click (kFromUserAgent, isTrusted:true)
- focus(el) - focus element
- hover(el) - dispatch mouseenter + mouseover
- type(el, text) - set value + fire input/change events
- check(el, bool?) - toggle/set checkbox or radio
- select(el, value) - select option in dropdown
- submit(form) - submit form via requestSubmit

Queries (pierce closed shadow DOM):
- query(selector) - deep querySelector
- queryAll(selector) - deep querySelectorAll

Read:
- attr(el, name) - get attribute
- setAttr(el, name, val) - set attribute
- text(el) - get textContent
- html(el) - get innerHTML
- value(el) - get input/select value

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
